Package: vigilaPeru
Title: Access Peru's National Epidemiological Surveillance Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Horacio", "ChacÃ³n Torrico", , "hchacont@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Description: Fast, reproducible access to Peru's national epidemiological surveillance 
    datasets (Ministry of Health / CDC-Peru) published on the Plataforma Nacional de 
    Datos Abiertos. Provides live CKAN API client functionality with caching, ready-made 
    helpers for malaria and dengue data, and lightning-fast aggregation with data.table.
